.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
House: cottage, gothic-revival, colonial, art-deco
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, poker, snooker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the person playing snooker is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the art-deco house is between the person playing poker and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the art-deco house and the person playing snooker##2
7. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
8. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the colonial house is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| House   | cottage      | gothic-revival  | art-deco  | colonial |
| Game           | snooker      | poker       | monopoly      | scrabble       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

