.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
City: rome, hannover, boston, new-york
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, time-travel, thriller, action
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the paramedic is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
6. the lawyer is the person watching action movies##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
8. the person traveling to rome is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching action movies##2
9. the person watching thriller movies is between the person traveling to boston and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| City        | hannover | boston     | rome   | new-york     |
| Movie-Genre       | time-travel   | horror   | thriller | action |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

