.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
City: new-york, nizza, miami, boston
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
4 different games are played: backgammon, poker, monopoly, bridge
 1. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
 2. the person traveling to boston is the fisherman##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person traveling to nizza is the police-officer##1
 8. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the person playing poker##1
10. the mechanic is between the owner of the bird and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| City   | boston | new-york  | miami | nizza       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Game         | backgammon | poker   | bridge   | monopoly         |

