.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, coffee, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, security-guard, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, marigold, sunflower, balloon-flower
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
 3. the security-guard is the person drinking milk##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 8. the lawyer is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage          | milk         | coffee         | cola     | almond-milk      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Flower         | zinnia     | sunflower       | balloon-flower | marigold |

