.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
House: art-deco, farmhouse, townhouse, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, mirinda, fanta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, sailing
1. the fan of folk is between the person who's sport is sailing and the fan of jazz##2
2. the farmhouse house is between the fan of folk and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person drinking almond-milk##2
4. the townhouse house is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the art-deco house##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| House           | townhouse | farmhouse | art-deco  | gothic-revival |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Beverage   | fanta   | almond-milk      | mirinda   | water   |
| Sport         | cycling   | sailing    | climbing | cricket   |

