.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, broccoli, pomegranate, lime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, analyst, entrepreneur, doctor
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, subway, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person eating broccoli is the entrepreneur##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the entrepreneur and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person driving the train##1
 5. the doctor is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 6. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the photographer is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
10. the entrepreneur is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | pomegranate | broccoli | banana  | lime  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Job   | photographer   | entrepreneur   | doctor | analyst |
| Transport     | airplane    | train   | bike    | subway  |

