3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person playing snooker is between the person playing go and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person who's sport is baseball is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
