.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, horse, ferret, hamster
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, fisherman, social-worker
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, chestnut, emerald, brown
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, parkour, volleyball
 1. the owner of the horse is the fisherman##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the fisherman is the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the person who likes brown is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the person who likes emerald is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
 9. the accountant is between the social-worker and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | hamster        | ferret    | mouse | horse   |
| Job           | social-worker | accountant | designer   | fisherman |
| Color   | emerald         | coral       | brown      | chestnut     |
| Sport         | parkour       | volleyball | cycling    | handball  |

