There 4 different types of food: corn, nectarine, onion, plum
House: tower, palace, townhouse, futuristic
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, rat, turtle
 1. the manager is on the right of the videographer##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the palace house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 4. the person eating corn is the videographer##1
 5. the architect is on the right of the project-manager##1
 6. the tower house is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the architect##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person eating plum is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the tower house is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Job   | videographer    | manager    | project-manager      | architect |
| Food       | corn        | plum       | onion       | nectarine     |
| House      | townhouse | tower | futuristic | palace        |
| Pet        | horse       | turtle     | rat         | dog           |

