The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, train, van
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the hamster##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is the person playing poker##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the train##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Game        | canasta  | poker | mah-jongg     | monopoly     |
| Pet         | hamster | goldfish | goat     | guinea-pig |
| City       | nizza  | hamburg   | san-francisco | rome    |
| Transport   | train   | subway   | jet-ski  | van        |

