The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, ice-hockey, handball, tennis
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 7. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's sport is handball##2
10. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |
